{"tid":1331473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賊人疑爆山頂獨立屋 被戶主撞破速逃","createTime":"2019-07-19T02:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T02:59:54.000Z","uid":3090,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b59e54e249d363dbd1770b6af41042f196953d50","tid":1331473,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rDqdXuA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDqdXuA.png&h=f4349a67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n山頂道東蘆一間獨立屋，凌晨近1時，一名男子懷疑潛入屋內爆竊，在花園被新加坡戶主發現，賊人立即爬過圍牆向山坡逃去。警方接報到場，在附近搜索沒有發現賊蹤，戶主點算並無損失。"}]}